h MZMs (TM). \\n\\n4. **Effective Hamiltonian**: The findings indicate that the low-energy-effective Hamiltonian behaves similarly to the two-channel Kondo model, leading to non-Fermi liquid excitations. The paper shows how perturbations that break symmetry can influence screening, yet certain protections remain intact at low temperatures.\\n\\n5. **Implications for Experimentation**: The results provide insights into the underlying physics essential for interpreting experimental measurements related to MZMs and Kondo systems. They open pathways for advancing both theoretical predictions and experimental verifications.\\n\\nThis comprehensive analysis of MZMs within the Majorana-Kondo system sheds light on critical interactions and provides a basis for future research in topological quantum computation and related fields.\", \"additional_kwargs\": {\"refusal\": null}, \"response_metadata\": {\"token_usage\": {\"completion_tokens\": 488, \"prompt_tokens\": 4435, \"total_tokens\": 4923, \"completion_tokens_details\": {\"accepted_prediction_tokens\": 0, \"audio_tokens\": 0, \"reasoning_tokens\": 0, \"rejected_prediction_tokens\": 0}, \"prompt_tokens_details\": {\"audio_tokens\": 0, \"cached_tokens\": 3328}}, \"model_provider\": \"openai\", \"model_name\": \"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\", \"system_fingerprint\": \"fp_373a14eb6f\", \"id\": \"chatcmpl-DCp66ri8UGRxtXpLbnAozGR8qC5tA\", \"service_tier\": \"default\", \"finish_reason\": \"stop\", \"logprobs\": null}, \"type\": \"ai\", \"id\": \"lc_run--019c905f-d759-70d3-b037-c1ebe4bcac51-0\", \"usage_metadata\": {\"input_tokens\": 4435, \"output_tokens\": 488, \"total_tokens\": 4923, \"input_token_details\": {\"audio\": 0, \"cache_read\": 3328}, \"output_token_details\": {\"audio\": 0, \"reasoning\": 0}}, \"tool_calls\": [], \"invalid_tool_calls\": []}}], \"evaluation\": {\"success\": true, \"needs_retry\": false, \"reason\": \"The user's request for a summary of the introduction and core contributions of the paper was successful